### MovementType
# @name MovementType_GET
GET {{server}}/movements-types/MovementType
Authorization: Basic {{username}}:{{password}}


### MovementType Drafts GET
# @name MovementType_Drafts_GET
GET {{server}}/movements-types/MovementType?$filter=(IsActiveEntity eq false)
Authorization: Basic {{username}}:{{password}}


### MovementType Draft POST
# @name MovementType_Draft_POST
POST {{server}}/movements-types/MovementType
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Basic {{username}}:{{password}}

