@draftID={{MovementType_Draft_POST.response.body.$.ID}}


### MovementType Draft PATCH
# @name MovementType_Draft_Patch
PATCH {{server}}/movements-types/MovementType(ID={{draftID}},IsActiveEntity=false)
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Basic {{username}}:{{password}}

